# Properties Panel Redesign (April 2026)

On 2026-04-03, the Properties panel was redesigned from an inline collapsible section into a slide-in side panel. On 2026-04-06, the header was restructured and a folder property row was added.

**Why:** The inline "Properties >" button took up vertical space in the note content area and was visually disconnected from the detail pane controls. Redesign integrates it as a proper inspector panel.

**How to apply:**

### Architecture

- `NoteMetadataSection` is a side panel with close button above "Properties" title
- Panel lives in ContentView's `singleNotePane` / `secondaryNotePane` via `propertiesPanelSlot()` helper
- Always-present in HStack (width animates 0<->340pt) -- avoids view insertion/removal jank
- Trigger: `.togglePropertiesPanel` notification (defined in Extensions.swift)
- State: `isPropertiesPanelVisible` + `propertiesPanelPane` in ContentView
- Todo toggle relayed via `.propertiesPanelToggleTodo` notification to NoteDetailView

### Header Layout (updated 2026-04-06)

- Close button (X): own `HStack` row, **left-aligned** (not right), above title
- Title "Properties": left-aligned, below close button

### Property Rows

- Created (date)
- **Folder** (updated 2026-04-06): receives full `Folder?` object (not just string name), renders colored pill with folder icon matching FloatingSearch's pill design. Uses `folder.folderColor` and `folder.folderColorNeedsDarkForeground` for theming.
- Tags (interactive: add/remove)
- Todos (expandable list with progress ring)
- Links (pill buttons)
- Attachments (pill buttons)
- Referenced By (backlinks, conditional)

### Button Placement

- Single pane: `.overlay(alignment: .topTrailing)` on `singleNotePane` -- hidden when panel is open
- Split view: last item in `splitPaneControls` HStack -- hidden when panel is open for that pane
- Icon: `IconSidebarLeftArrow` (15x15 SVG, flipped horizontally for close button inside panel)
- Custom glass tooltip (below icon, `.bottomTrailing` alignment, y: +34)

### Animation

- `.spring(response: 0.3, dampingFraction: 0.82)` -- defined as `ContentView.propertiesPanelAnimation`
- Combined effects: width (0->340), scale (0.78/0.88->1), blur (6->0), opacity (0->1)
- Anchor: `.trailing` for scale effect
- No `.transition()` used -- animation driven entirely by `withAnimation` + property interpolation

### Performance Fix (Split View)

- Root cause: `.animation(.easeInOut(duration: 0.15), value: previewingVersion?.id)` was on the HStack in `secondaryNotePane`, causing entire NoteDetailView to re-layout on every panel animation frame
- Fix: moved that `.animation()` to the ZStack inside the HStack (scoped to version preview only), matching `singleNotePane`'s structure via `detailPane()`
- `bottomFadeGradient` made `static let` to avoid recomputation during animation frames

### Color Tokens Added

- `TodoContainerColor`: #D6D3D1 light / #292524 dark (matches tabs container fill) -- used for todo pill, todo list, tag pills
- `TodoProgressGhostColor`: #FFFFFF light / #0C0A09 dark -- currently unused, replaced by `TodoProgressColor.opacity(0.2/0.35)` inline
